dc_description_s: This data represents building footprints for Washburn County, Wisconsin in 2026.[The Building Footprints layer helps to provide polygon data for structural buildings that exist within Washburn County. It was created using previous data, land records information, and historical imagery. The data contains polygon features within Washburn County as well as the primary source for creating the footprint, max min and mean z-values, shape length and area, and editor information. The building footprints layer is updated and maintained continuously using the most current and available aerial photography and ArcGIS tools.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
